    "Only explicitly documented values were recorded. No values computed from other angles.",
    "Vehicle KE vs Absorbed: A-SAFE documents a single 'Max Energy (Joules)' figure per angle that represents both the vehicle KE at impact and the energy the barrier is tested to withstand (100% transfer). Where this single figure is stated we recorded it in both rating{angle}Absorbed and rating{angle}VehicleKE."
